reviewText:
This game is great so im going to keep this short so I can play more.
Pros
Super fast download {literally like 1 min from clicking download to actually playing.}
Game doesnt have a steep learning curve {about as steep as a Mc Donolds playground slide.}
Gameplay is solid and doesnt require a super gamming computer to play.
Cons
No sound track and limited sound effects {not a big con I just play a youtube video over the game.}
The game has a mild grind but nothing that is super bad {I had two ships after two hours.}
If you dont like reading you better start likeing it because there is a bit of reading too do in the beggining missions.

All in all this game is good for those who want a free fun game.
